-- FBR Adds 29 From Lazard Capital Markets for Investment Bank
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2013-10-14T20:36:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-14/fbr-adds-29-from-lazard-capital-markets-for-investment-bank.html
FBR & Co. (FBRC) , the middle-market
investment firm, added 29 professionals from Lazard Capital
Markets after the closely held brokerage said it was exploring
strategic alternatives.  FBR hired six senior research analysts, six sales traders,
three position traders and four institutional sales people, the
Arlington, Virginia-based firm said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
